latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We have worked mainly to pop her eyes and lift her glamour.

To add the strength to her innocent eyes, we mixed smoke and glitters. Her magenta outfit is perfectly matched with partial Smokey shadows and different shades of purple glitters.

We have kept her foundation, Blush and highlights to neutral side. The lips are given natural pink touch.

Hair is left free to wave over shoulders. So that she can flirt with it while dropping the eyelids and play the magic.

This is one of the shades of our glam looks focused on neutral glowing skin and sparkling Smokey eyes.

Such make up is today’s generation demand where they want Hollywood touch in their looks for the day or night parties.
